                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TEC-0049</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8744 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西广电网络机顶盒技术创新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STB technological innovation process of Shaanxi Broadcast &amp;amp;TV Network</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李纯青，马军平等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西广电网络传媒（集团）股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新闻出版业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西广电网络；机顶盒；技术创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shaanxi Broadcast &amp;amp; TV Network；set - top box（STB）；technological innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西广电网络传媒（集团）股份有限公司（简称陕西广电网络）是全国首家实现全省广电网络整合的省级广电网络公司。公司2007年启动系统建设提出技术创新，2008年在全国率先创建了“风险共担、利益共享”的有线数字电视应用技术实验室。实验室吸纳了国内外20多个著名研究院所、高校、系统集成商、软件开发商和设备生产商。成功研发出了全国首台统一软、硬件方案的数字电视机顶盒，不仅为公司数字机顶盒整转节约了上亿元成本，而且大大加快数字化转换进度，为数字电视多功能、多业务开发和双向化发展创造了条件。更重要的是为公司培育了技术研发队伍、打造了技术创新的技术平台，为此，国家广电总局特批将“有线数字电视应用技术实验室”设在陕西广电网络。本案例描述了陕西广电网络公司机顶盒技术创新的整个过程，详细讲述了公司是在怎样的情况下大胆推进技术创新，构建创新组织机构并形成研发机制，打破数字电视机顶盒“七国八制十二侯”的局面，为公司未来发展奠定了先机。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Shaanxi Broadcast &amp; TV Network Intermediary Group Co.,Ltd.( Shaanxi Broadcast &amp; TV network)is a large state-owned culture and media corporate group, and the first provincial broadcast &amp; TV network group in China to integrate these two networks. The company advance technological innovation in 2007, and has the only “Cable and digital TV Application Technology Lab” in China, which is named by SAPPRFT(State Administration of Press, Publication, Radio, Film and Television). The lab has attracted more than 20 domestic and overseas research institutes and universities, system integrators, software developers and equipment manufacturers.  The lab have developed successfully the unified standards STB(set - top box) in China, the application of which driving the rapid development of the broadcasting and TV network. The most important is the lab has become a technological innovation organization. The case describes the STB technological innovation process of Shaanxi Broadcast &amp;TV network. The case give a detailed account of how did the company do on technological innovation. And approach to the problem of Multiple standards. Emphasis are focuse on the development of innovation organization of company, which helpful to the future development of the company. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
